/-- The Weierstrass ‚Ñò function with the `l‚ÇÄ`-term missing.
This is mainly a tool for calculations where one would want to omit a diverging term. -/
def ‚ÑòExcept (l‚ÇÄ : ‚ÑÇ) (z : ‚ÑÇ) : ‚ÑÇ :=
